.SH STANDARDS
4.3BSD.
This function is deprecated (marked as LEGACY in POSIX.1-2001): use
.BR memcpy (3)
or
.BR memmove (3)
in new programs.
Note that the first two arguments
are interchanged for
.BR memcpy (3)
and
.BR memmove (3).
POSIX.1-2008 removes the specification of
.BR bcopy ().
